                "text_dRcppE": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p><strong>Printed in-house</strong><br/>Every edition is printed on our risograph in Barcelona using soy-based inks and sustainably sourced paper. Your customers are getting something genuinely handmade.</p><p><strong>Artist-led, every time</strong><br/>Every product is made in collaboration with a credited artist. We work with emerging and established illustrators and artists from around the world, so your range stays varied and always worth looking at.</p><p><strong>Small runs, high desirability</strong><br/>We produce limited editions on purpose. Low stock levels mean your customers know they're getting something worth owning before it's gone.</p><p><strong>One supplier, many styles</strong><br/>From artist books and zines to apparel and objects, you can carry a varied range of aesthetics and formats, all from one place.</p>",
